title: Beach Bites with Katie Lee S01E01 Doing the Island Hop PDTV.x264
description:
On this gourmet getaway, Katie Lee crosses sand and surf in search of the best beach foods to dive into, with the best views to match. She follows her taste buds to find delicious dishes, and along the way meets the chefs serving up the finest fare that the shores have to offer.




Beach Bites with Katie Lee - Season 1, Episode 1


Doing the Island Hop

From St. Thomas to Mackinac Island, Michigan to Montauk, New York, Katie Lee is beach hopping to find the local take on the best treats these islands have to offer. Plus, there's always time for cocktails, sweet treats, and more on this island hopping adventure!


Original Air Date: 02-Jun-2016
